'''Saxaro''' sidoo kale loo yaqaano '''Xaar''' ({{lang-ar|روث, سماد}} {{lang-it|letame ''ama'' stallatico}} {{lang-en|manure}}) waa qashinka ka soo baxa [[dad]]ka, [[xoolo|xoolaha]] iyo gebi ahaanba [[xayawaan]]ka noocyadiisa kala duwan. 

Saxaradu waa hadhaaga [[cunto|cuntada]], midaas oo marka [[calool|calooshu]] shiido loo kala saaro nafaqo [[jidh]]ku awood ka helo iyo qashin xaga dambe laga soo saaro. 

Saxarada [[xoolo|xoolaha]] iyo [[xayawaan]]ka waxaa loo yaqaanaa '''Digo'''. 

Maadaama saxaradu ka samaysan tahay [[macdan]] kala duwan oo u badan [[isku dhis]]yo [[kaarboon]] ah, waxay nafaqo fiican siisaa [[caro|carada]]. 
